@database SG&SMTK.GUIDE
@node MAIN "Guide for SG&S3Mouse/Time/Key version"

	Before reading this you shuld read ScreenGrab&Save3.0.GUIDE!

	@{"SG&S3Mouse" link E-M}
	@{"SG&S3Time " link E-T}
	@{"SG&S3Key  " link E-K}

	Pre ovoga trebalo bi da procitate ScreenGrab&Save3.0.GUIDE!

	@{"SG&S3Mouse" link S-M}
	@{"SG&S3Time " link S-T}
	@{"SG&S3Key  " link S-K}

@endnode
@node E-M "Mouse version"

	Program is almost the same but works using mouse!
	Diference is: only two Cycle Gadgets.

	Right - options for right mouse button
	Left - options for left mouse button


	NOTE! There is small bug with this! No mater what port you chose
	right mouse always do what is defined for him!

	Hotkey for this version of SG&S is lalt+lshift+m

@endnode
@node E-T "Time"

	In this version all you need to do is to set time in secods.
	It works this way:

	- If you set 5 sec then SG&S waits for 5 sec then saves both IFF and
BitMap and DISABLE him self.
	- If you set 10 sec then SG&S wait 5 sec to pass,saves,then wait for
10 sec to pass,saves and DISABLE him self.
	- If it is seted 15 sec then:wait 5,saves,wait another 10,saves again
wait for last 15 sec,saves and QUITS.
	It is same with all other values.Values are: 5,10,15,20,25,30,60,90 
and 120 seconds.

	Before you chose ENABLE select PAL or NTSC(depending from your game
screen)!Time waiting are difrent for PAL/NTSC screens!
	Hotkey for this one is lalt+lshift+t
@endnode
@node E-K "Keys"

	This is easy for conrol.When you ENABLE him keys to use are:

	I - saves IFF image
	B - saves BitMap
	F - show interFace
	W - force opening Workbench
	Q - Quit/DISABLE SG&S
	D - like Q
	

	Hotkey for this one is lalt+lshift+k
@endnode
@node S-M "Mis verzija"

	Program je gotovo indentican ali koristi misa!
	Razlika je: samo dva ciklicna gadzeta.

	Right - definise rad desnog dugmeta misa.
	Left - definise rad levog dugmeta misa.

	PAZNJA!Postoji mali 'bag' sa ovim!Bez obzira koji port odaberete,
	desno dugme ce uvek raditi sta je definisano u SG&S-u!

	'Hotkey' za ovu verziju je lalt+lshift+m
@endnode
@node S-T "Vreme"

	Sve sto treba da uradite je da podesite vreme u sekundama.
	Radi na sledeci nacin:

	- Ako podesite na 5 sekundi onda SG&S ceka 5 sekundi a zatim usnimava
IFF sliku i BitMap-u,a zatim se iskljucuje automatski.
	- Ako podesite na 10 sekundi,SG&S prvo ceka 5 sekundi,zatim usnimava,
ceka novih 10 sekundi,usnimava i iskljucuje se.
	- Ako podesite 15,SG&S ceka 5 sekundi,usnimava,ceka novih 10 sekundi,
usnimava,i zatim ceka posledjih 15 sekundi,usnimava i iskljucuje se.
	Za sve ostale vrednosti je isto.Na raspolaganju su 5,10,15,20,30,60,
90 i 120 sekundi.
	Pre ukljucenja na ENABLE,izaberite PAL ili NTSC (u zavisnosti od 
ekrana koji igra koristi)!Vrednosti proteklog vremena se razlikuju za
PAL/NTSC rezolucije.

	'Hotkey' je lalt+lshift+t
@endnode
@node S-K "Tasteri"

	Lak za kontrolu.Kada kliknete na ENABLE koristite tastere:

	I - snima IFF sliku
	B - Snima BitMap-u
	F - otvara 'interFejs'
	W - otvara Workbench
	Q - iskljucuje se
	D - kao kod Q

	'Hotkey' je lalt+lshift+k
@endnode
